<plot>Each year tourists come to southern Montana from all over the world to be a part of the annual celebrations marking the anniversary of Custer's Last Stand. "Dying With Custer" is a sometimes poignant, sometimes comical look at the way we remember history, and what that memory has to say about who we are.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?162907</url></doc>
